astly\noutperforms strict process isolation in terms of performance. In our security\nevaluation, we show that Dynamic Process Isolation statistically provides the\nsame security guarantees as strict process isolation, fully mitigating Spectre\nattacks between multiple tenants.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Oct 2021 10:12:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-12"}
